The paper focuses on detecting and analyzing resource leak bugs in Android apps, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the implementation of a static checker, which relates to the computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) and systems and control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Finally, the empirical study and data mining aspects of the paper could also be relevant to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
